name: Found Someone You Have & Higher Ground
Text: 'During a battle at opponent''s site (or your non-<> site), instead of firing one of your character weapons at a target, cause that target to be immunity to attrition -3 (or limited to immunity to attrition < 5) for remainder of turn. OR Find one of your missing characters. OR Cancel a ''react.'' OR Once per game, use 1 Force to exchange a card in hand with the top most character of ability < 5 in your Lost Pile.',
